18%2F06%2F20%2F103133_bbdc6fbf548bca3d9bca28856035cb5f.png&h=cf62b0fa&s={SIZE}\" />，"},{"pid":"b565675670270b52ac004b55f023dacbb458c6e1","tid":709343,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:34:50.000Z","msg":"原post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/702840/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/702840/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180618/58333332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F58333332&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3b19a1ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F58333332&h=e547abff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180618/58333332</a>"},{"pid":"72b590b6b86e88c25cbeb501030ebeba96a6cc82","tid":709343,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"MOM!"},{"pid":"5effa481f9bd76b399dbfa67dbaabcd2ada53a0c","tid":709343,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:52:34.000Z","msg":"新屯門中心發生三屍倫常慘案，剛大學畢業女生，疑不堪濕疹困擾，疑在父親節先以利刀手刃雙親，再以膠袋笠頭注入氦氣自殺身亡。疑似女死者在討論區發文問「氦氣自殺有冇得諗」。除了發文外，疑似女死者兩個月前亦有回答並他網民的濕疹問題，更透露「今次真係好難捱，鎖埋自己係房唔出街，就嚟自殺。」<br />\n<br />\n疑似女死者的網民在「連登」討論區曾發文問「氦氣自殺有冇得諗」，除了發文外，該名網民亦在其他有關濕疹的帖文回覆，分享自己治療濕疹的經歷，指服用類固醇反彈辛苦過濕疹很多，指她現時正經歷這個情況，「以前濕疹幾辛苦都捱得過，但今次真係好難捱，鎖埋自己係房唔出街，就嚟自殺。」<br />\n<br />\n她續指：「起碼反彈半年先穩定，而家啲皮膚已經唔係正常皮膚，連燈都唔想開，鏡都唔想照，我唔會介意人地目光，我只會介意自己啲皮膚舒唔舒服，只要好得番，我理得自己全身疤痕黑印」。"},{"pid":"a3d1543f567ab9cc25fee975a34b5bc3a8d68586","tid":709343,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"#4607<br />\n資深會員"},{"pid":"4f112caee1b9cc9cc75ae2431f1ebfcf8f9ee79d","tid":709343,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:18:25.000Z","msg":"RIP